lyrics:
[Verse]
Smokin' blunts on the block, Gangster rap never stops
2Pac vibes, I'm the king on the top
Living life in a struggle, gotta hustle everyday
I'm the voice of the streets, let my words convey

[Chorus]
Lofi DnB flow, takin' you real low
Gangster rap lyrics, filled with stories untold
Laid-back beats, keepin' it smooth and slow
This is how we roll, in the world we call home
